reviews.review:
Funny game, pretty cool to play with friends or even alone and have fun.

But a few things that must be reworked:

-rank: the rank they fixed on crossplay (good job, thumbs up to devs);
-hitbox: is pretty shit and makes you want to hit the monitor sometimes;
-rewards: play to get almost only bloodpoints is kinda boring... the cellphone have more stuffs to make you keep on playing;
